# Privacy Policy for RSS for PowerToys Command Palette

**Last Updated: April 4, 2025**

## Introduction

Thank you for choosing our RSS for PowerToys Command Palette application ("App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing you with a secure experience. This Privacy Policy explains our approach to data handling when you use our completely RSS for PowerToys Command Palette application.

Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By downloading, accessing, or using our App, you agree to the terms described in this policy.

## Offline Functionality

Our RSS Reader can operate offline. This means:

- All data, including your RSS feed URLs, content, and settings, is stored exclusively on your local device
- No personal information is transmitted to our servers or any third parties
- We do not collect, access, or process any of your data remotely

## Information Stored Locally

The following information is stored locally on your device only:

- **RSS Feed URLs**: The RSS feed URLs you add to the App
- **RSS Content**: Content downloaded from these sources during refresh operations
- **User Preferences**: Your preferences regarding display settings, refresh intervals, and other customization options
- **Reading Status**: Information about which articles you have read or saved

## Data Security

Since all data is stored locally on your device:
- The security of your information depends on your device's security
- Uninstalling the App will remove all App-related data from your device
- We recommend keeping your device's operating system updated for optimal security

## Internet Access

While the App requires internet access to fetch content from RSS feeds, this communication is:
- Directly between your device and the RSS feed providers
- Not routed through or monitored by our servers
- Not used to collect any personal information

## Third-Party Content

Our App displays content from the RSS feeds you choose to add. Please note:
- Content displayed comes directly from third-party RSS providers
- We have no control over the content or links within these RSS feeds
- External websites accessed through links in RSS content have their own privacy policies

## Children's Privacy

Our App is not directed to children under the age of 13. Since we do not collect any personal information, there is minimal risk to children who may use the App.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on the Microsoft Store page and updating the "Last Updated" date.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.

## Consent

By using our App, you consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.